&lt;li&gt;Write and refine&amp;nbsp;briefs, messaging, story angles and toolkits, ensuring ideas are insight-driven and culturally relevant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with creative, strategy, social and production teams to&amp;nbsp;shape and stress test&amp;nbsp;ideas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee&amp;nbsp;content development, from press materials and social copy to influencer briefs and event concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and coordinate activity across&amp;nbsp;multiple markets or regions&amp;nbsp;when required, ensuring consistency&lt;/li&gt;
