&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is passionate about client servicing, media relations and outreach and to develop any other relationships that are beneficial to our clients. The ideal candidate will have versatile PR experience, a solid network of corporate communications&#39; media contacts, and be fluent in both Cantonese and English is a must. (Mandarin would be great, too!)&lt;/p&gt;
