&lt;p&gt;• Provide excellent media relations expertise and outreach.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Understand what themes and content will drive coverage and conversations; develop relevant narratives and media pitches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Learn about data to craft and implement integrated strategies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Work with content and design teams to craft best in class content and media materials.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Working to foster strong relationships with industry Media and Influencers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Monitor and track client, competitor, industry, and cultural news and share with team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Coordinate logistics for online and virtual events&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
