&lt;p&gt;• Native Cantonese speaker and strong written, spoken and comprehension of English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Driven, smart and a go-getter with a passion for communication industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Meticulous and detail oriented, yet able to work fast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Collaborative work style&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
