&lt;p&gt;Golin Hong Kong has been awarded four accolades in the past two years for our commitment to people, culture, benefits, and DEI approach, by leading industry bodies Campaign Asia, PR Week Asia and PRospect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ethos is simple yet powerful: we&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Go All In&lt;/strong&gt;. It’s why we’ve also won over 16 awards for our client work in the past two years. Our teams are curious, creative, brave, inclusive and driven. If that sounds like somewhere you want to work, then read on!&lt;/p&gt;
