&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;WHO WE’RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic Director to lead our high performing PR team; a hunter, a collaborator, a leader, a motivator and a problem solver. The candidate should be thoughtful and accountable with a deliberate plan of action that they execute and are measured against. They succeed by taking their extensive PR expertise and integrating it with the other marketing disciplines within Golin and beyond to win exciting new integrated work for the agency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will lead a portfolio of clients in&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;tech, arts, travel and lifestyle&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;across brand promotion and corporate reputation.&lt;/p&gt;
