&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a passion for working in consumer health and wellbeing?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get excited pitching to media and building relationships with journalists?&lt;/li&gt;
