&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Then you might just be the Senior Account Manager we are looking for!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Golin is recruiting an ambitious Senior Account Manager to join our Consumer Health team. From using humour and entertainment to challenge the stigma around hearing loss, to developing a PE kit to empower girls to stay active, to partnering with a global superstar to encourage people to access mental health therapy - our work is bold, creative, culturally relevant and, most importantly, meaningful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a media savvy Senior Account Manager to join our Consumer Health team and work on leading consumer health and wellbeing brands. The ideal candidate will have excellent media relations expertise and contacts, particularly with consumer lifestyle, wellbeing and health journalists. The role involves counselling clients on media strategy, curating stories, managing a team to generate earned media coverage, managing high profile consumer campaign launches as well as managing a range of experts and influencers from KOLs to celebrity talent and conducting research projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity to work on well-known consumer health brands, playing a central role to deliver impactful earned-media strategies and award-winning creative campaigns.&lt;/p&gt;
