&lt;li&gt;Review others’ work and provide clear direction on how content may be improved&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use your understanding of the media landscape to target journalists and strategies to gain the best cut-through when selling in, and share media knowledge with junior team members&lt;/li&gt;
