&lt;li&gt;Take personal responsibility for the day-to-day delivery of projects against agreed plans and budget, proactively flagging any changes or delays to clients with solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support senior leads in financial oversight and management of projects, including budget trackers, invoicing, budgeting and forecasting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seek out opportunities for organic growth with existing clients and support senior team in the development of new business pitches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
