&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT US&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Golin is a global public relations agency that helps companies create change that matters. For more than 60 years, we’ve redefined the role of PR with bold, data-driven creativity that earns real business and societal impact. In 2025, Golin was named PRWeek Global Agency of the Year, Best Agency Asia Pacific, and Champion Agency of the Year at the Marketing PR Awards Asia – a testament to our consistent excellence across markets and disciplines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We made history in 2024 as the first PR agency to win a Cannes Lions Grand Prix, alongside a Gold and three Silver Lions. That same year, PRovoke named us Asia-Pacific Digital Consultancy of the Year, following our 2023 recognition as Best Large Consultancy to Work For – based on feedback from our own people. Our Asia-established Creative Intelligence Unit was named Specialist Consultancy of the Year by the PR Awards Asia in both 2023 and 2024, reinforcing our leadership in innovative, insights-led communications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We proudly serve some of the world’s most influential brands, offering a full suite of services including content creation and production, influencer marketing, corporate and consumer strategy, public affairs, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For over 25 years, we’ve been creating impact across Asia with teams in Shanghai, Beijing, Hong Kong, Singapore, Taipei, Jakarta, Mumbai, Delhi, Bangalore, Kuala Lumpur, Seoul, and Tokyo. Guided by our mission of Creating Change in Asia for Asia, we champion meaningful outcomes – from award-winning travel campaigns and pioneering comms tools to purpose-led advocacy that drives real legislative and social progress. Every initiative is designed to make change matter – for our clients, communities, people, and the industry at large.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re also future-focused. Golin is on a bold path to becoming the &lt;strong&gt;first fully AI-integrated global PR agency by 2026&lt;/strong&gt;, equipping and enabling every employee, across every role, level, and location, to harness AI and unlock their full human potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Singapore, we drive regional excellence through a collaborative team of specialists in data analytics, creative intelligence, content production, performance marketing, consumer activation, stakeholder engagement, and reputation management. We foster a culture of bravery, empowerment, and accountability that pushes boundaries and delivers results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ethos is simple yet powerful: &lt;strong&gt;We Go All In.&lt;/strong&gt; For our clients. For our colleagues. For our agency. For our industry. If that sounds like something you’d wake up every morning excited to be part of, read on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO WE’RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager/Manager&lt;/strong&gt; who’s ready to shape reputations, build trust, and spark business impact for some of the world’s most ambitious brands. You’ll play a central role in driving integrated communications programmes that fuse corporate storytelling with digital innovation. You’re not just comfortable navigating complex business and technology narratives—you thrive on turning them into campaigns that matter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES: &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Give best-in-class corporate reputation advice and strategic direction for clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead fully integrated campaigns that blend earned, social, and digital to tell compelling stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee day-to-day account work and see campaigns through from end to end for global and regional corporate and technology brands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fuse corporate reputation with digital, creative, and technology communications solutions, working with our kick-ass creatives and strategists to deliver effective campaigns and res

&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Manager, you play an essential role in creating change for our clients. You drive our clients’ business as a brand/business steward. You ensure we’re delivering the maximum impact in leading and managing accounts for the agency. And, are responsible for the Golin brand with clients. You are curious, creative, brave, inclusive and collaborative. And, are passionate about driving results. You are relevance obsessed and flawless in your execution. In a nutshell, you’re a progressive business driver.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Manager, you own it. You are the day-to-day manager of client programs, deliverables and campaigns. You are the “go to” for your team members as well as subject matter experts. You have a clear understanding of your client’s business and our role in keeping “the train on the tracks.” You are not only reactive but proactive as you anticipate problems and solutions. And, you are sharing your expertise with more junior talent. You provide real-time coaching and demonstrate inclusive behavior to help others succeed. You use your time wisely and prioritize what’s most important.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the corporate PR/communications initiatives, managing a combination of clients within our wide portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate mastery of details and coordination by managing program planning – research budgets, manage timelines, participate in brainstorms, manage vendor relationships and track budgets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish a strong rapport with top-tier business and media members, and be able to identify and familiarize with key trade editors and correspondents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop media strategies, and be involved in the development of various materials such as pitch letters, key messages, press release, Q&amp;amp;A etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn broadly about client’s business, outside of communications and day-to-day needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with content and design teams to craft best in class content and media materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Provide guidance and mentorship to junior team members while fostering a cohesive team spirit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
